               GUILTY
            </rs>, <rs id="t18020918-67-punish351" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18020918-67-punish351" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020918-67-defend509 t18020918-67-punish351"></join>
               Death
            </rs>, aged 25.</p>
               <p>The prisoner was recommended, by the Jury, to his Majesty's mercy, on account of his good behaviour.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Le Blanc.</p>
